+Agent Fox Technical Core V1B-1C
+
+Mission: ENG-20260722-142022-9FAE11
+
+Purpose
+-------
+Compare the authoritative qualified minimal-load and normal-loaded
+resource evidence without performing another live scan.
+
+The component verifies all eight source files by exact SHA-256, verifies
+both qualification states and capture-receipt relationships, then writes
+exactly five deterministic outputs into the mission evidence directory.
+
+This component does not inspect live processes or ports, start or stop
+anything, connect to the network, import live FOXAI modules, modify the
+source evidence, modify WebUI or Desktop integration, diagnose the PC,
+issue tuning or purchasing recommendations, or access rollback drive K:.
+
+The report distinguishes direct observations, arithmetic derivations,
+bounded interpretations, and known limitations.
